# Setup pipeline

**Order:** Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and set secrets → Run `./start.sh` → Add gateways in Admin UI → Configure Cursor (JWT + mcp.json) → Restart Cursor.

**CI** runs on push/PR: lint (shellcheck + ruff), test (pytest), Docker build, gateway health smoke. See [.github/workflows/ci.yml](../../.github/workflows/ci.yml).

